title: 2face Idibia: Protesters say music star is a 'Chicken'
text:
2face Idibia over the weekend pulled out of a nationwide protest against bad governance which he had championed. play 2face protest (Pulse) The protest is currently holding at the Nationa Stadium, Surulere, Lagos and protesters have expressed their frustration and anger over the 'Oya come make we go' singer's pull out.
